      <title>各大银行探索发行与七国集团货币挂钩的稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/major-banks-explore-issuing-stablecoins-pegged-g7-currencies-2025-10-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行、德意志银行、高盛、瑞银等十家主要银行正在联合探索发行稳定币，这是传统金融寻求应对数字资产增长的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/major-banks-explore-issuing-stablecoins-pegged-g7-currencies-2025-10-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Oct 2025 13:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
